OL,3,CIslanders petition to stop conversion
OL,4,Cof Jersey Airport viewing area
OL,6,FA petition has been launched to stop
OL,7,FJersey Airport from converting its
OL,8,Fviewing area along with the
OL,9,Fintroduction of a No 1 Lounge.
OL,11,FSo far the petition on Jersey
OL,12,Fgovernment's website has more than 250
OL,13,Fsignatures.
OL,15,FThe petition claims: "Jersey Airport
OL,16,Fis converting the free-to-use upstairs
OL,17,Fviewing platform in the departures
OL,18,Farea into a paid-for lounge.
