OL,6,FThe petition wants the seating area to
OL,7,Fbe "preserved for future generations
OL,8,Fto enjoy at no extra cost".
OL,10,FPorts of Jersey states: "We hope to
OL,11,Fcreate an 'open to all' roof terrace
OL,12,Fbetween the old and new terminal
OL,13,Fbuildings, a fun play area for
OL,14,Fchildren, as well as a quieter area
OL,15,Fthat will provide a calm environment
OL,16,Ffor passengers seeking somewhere
OL,17,Fpeaceful away from the hustle and
OL,18,Fbustle of the airport.
